

'''= developing a collaborative, open source, network building tool to organize and share notes and research.'''

URL = http://thewikinetsproject.wordpress.com/

=Description=

"What is WikiNets? Well, just an idea so far. But soon, we hope, it will be an online tool for piecing ideas together into a graphical form that is easy to read, understand, remember, and analyse. It will do this by providing a platform for the collaborative creation of annotated networks for some chosen topic, with the nodes in each network representing all relevant variables, and the connections between them describing how they are related. Imagine a streamlined Wikipedia, we’ve been telling people, one built to focus on the links."
(http://thewikinetsproject.wordpress.com/2013/07/05/it-begins/)


